<Prose>
	<h2>Senior Software & DevOps Engineer shipping end-to-end</h2>
	<p>
		Berlin-based builder with 15+ years of experience delivering high-reliability systems at scale. I specialize in transforming complex technical challenges into production-ready solutions—from monolith-to-microservices migrations that cut deployment times from hours to minutes, to architecting platforms processing high transaction volumes. I thrive in remote, async environments and champion AI-augmented workflows to accelerate delivery cycles.
	</p>

	<h3>What I'm doing right now</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Senior DevOps engineer/consultant embedded in SRE and platform teams, driving infrastructure resilience across mission-critical systems.</li>
		<li>Orchestrating operations for microservices handling substantial daily transaction volumes while reducing incident response time.</li>
		<li>Architecting developer tooling and internal platforms that accelerate release cycles and unblock feature teams.</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Track record</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Led monolith-to-microservices migrations for B2B/B2C platforms serving hundreds of thousands of users.</li>
		<li>Engineered SSO and registration systems for millions of monthly active users.</li>
		<li>Built data-intensive services processing terabytes of data with excellent availability.</li>
		<li>Pioneered infrastructure-as-code practices reducing provisioning time from days to hours.</li>
		<li>Experience across transportation, PropTech, FinTech, and postal services sectors.</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>How I like to work</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>End-to-end ownership: design, implementation, instrumentation, rollout, and the follow-up fixes that make things robust.</li>
		<li>Start with the problem, baseline with metrics, ship a thin slice, and watch the numbers before widening rollout.</li>
		<li>Write concise RFCs, prefer async collaboration, and pair when velocity or clarity needs it.</li>
		<li>Enjoy deleting code and simplifying flows once the signal is clear.</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Stack and tools I reach for</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Languages: TypeScript/JavaScript, Rust, Java, Kotlin, Go, Scala, Python, Bash.</li>
		<li>Frameworks: React, Astro, Spring, Ktor, Play Framework, Axum.</li>
		<li>Ops: Kubernetes/OpenShift, AWS/Azure, Terraform/CloudFormation/Ansible, Grafana/Loki/Prometheus/Splunk.</li>
		<li>Delivery: Helm/Kustomize/Timoni, GitHub Actions/GitLab CI/Jenkins, feature flags, observability first.</li>
		<li>Databases: PostgreSQL, Oracle, MongoDB, Elasticsearch, Redis.</li>
	</ul>

